{"tid":2165960,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone SE 熱賣效應   Apple Watch 明年傳推 SE 版","createTime":"2020-08-20T06:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T08:15:17.000Z","uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"47575d8a1c409d80141f777191f6cea425fd23ff","tid":2165960,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇晒心電圖呢D功能已經冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係冇咩錢<br />\n我寧願買S4好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年上市的新版 iPhone SE 熱賣，讓 Apple 找到了一條吸引中低階市場消費者的門路，就是以舊款設計和部份舊款零件，搭配最新的處理器，再以相對貼地的中階定位吸客。這招數據說會在明年複製，但會應用於 Apple Watch 之上。<br />\n<br />\n現時 Apple Watch 已經是市佔率最高的智能手錶，但有指 Apple 希望將智能手錶產品擴展至 iPhone 和 AirPods 的規模，於是有意推出一款相對便宜的 Apple Watch SE 以吸引更多人選購。消息指 Apple Watch SE 將會採用 Apple Watch Series 3 的外形，但採用跟今年稍後推出 Apple Watch Series 6 相同的 S6 處理器，搭配 16GB 儲存、藍牙 5.0 和有 4G 連線版本。<br />\n<br />\n部份高階功能，例如心電圖、Always-on 螢幕都會被拿走，Apple Watch SE 據說亦只會提供 42mm 一種尺寸。Apple Watch SE 預計會在明年 3 月推出，售價將會跟現時 Apple Watch Series 3 的定價相同，普通版為 HK$1,699，而 4G 版本則售 HK$2,499。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：cnbeta<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/27347/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1141%2F27347%2F1%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=544f233c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/27347/1/</a>"},{"pid":"780583ac568ffd359c51716380b30de1d6b51cb4","tid":2165960,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T14:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce041f204130140ce08ec363844c28f9b2bc96c8","tid":2165960,"uid":226155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"HK$1,699咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img